{"lemma":"رِيقِ","slug":"رِيقِ","root":"ر.#.ق","root_slug":"ر-_-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-_-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17114","n17290","n17121","n17295","n17291"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"saliva, spittle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a time of freshness and vigor","examples":[{"text":"فِي رَيِّق الشَّبَاب","english":"in the full bloom of youth"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew רוק (roq)"},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17114","headword_ar":"رَيْقٌ","root":"rwq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places, in the former half of the paragraph: ―         -b2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riy~iqN","text_ar":"رِيِّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17290","headword_ar":"رَيْقٌ","root":"ryq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A shining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) of a sword [&c.]. (TA.) Hence, in a trad. respecting [the battle of] Bedr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_i*aA birayoqi sayofK mino waraAy^iY","text_ar":"فَاـِذَا بِرَيْقِ سَيْفٍ مِنْ وَرَايِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And lo, the shining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistening, of a sword behind me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: thus written by El-Wákidee: if the reading"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyqu","text_ar":"بَرِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa","text_ar":"بَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] had been transmitted, it would be evidently reasonable. (IAth, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baATilN","text_ar":"بَاطِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"False,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vain, speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conduct"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoSiro Eano rayoqika","text_ar":"اَقْصِرْ عَنْ رَيْقِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Desist thou from thy false,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vain, speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conduct"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoqu All~ayoli","text_ar":"رَيْقُ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h [to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraAb","text_ar":"سَرَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mirage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoqN","text_ar":"رَيْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or water"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is drunk in the state of fasting, in the early morning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part of the day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [and] so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iqN","text_ar":"رَايِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is [said to be] not applied [in this sense] to anything but water: you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N raAy^iqN","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ رَايِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) [But see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iqN","text_ar":"رَايِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xubozN rayoqN","text_ar":"خُبْزٌ رَيْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iqN","text_ar":"رَايِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, JK, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dry bread;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bread without seasoning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condiment, to render it pleasant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savoury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, JK, IDrd, K.) ―         -b6-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ray~iqN","text_ar":"رَيِّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": both are also mentioned in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwq","text_ar":"روق"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v."}],"source_refs":["K","TA","IDrd","As","JK"]},{"entry_id":"n17121","headword_ar":"رَيِّقٌ","root":"rwq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places, in the former half of the paragraph. ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most excellent"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything; (JK, S;) as, for instance, of wine, or beverage, and of rain. (JK.) ―         -b3-  And it is said to signify also, (JK, Ibn-'Abbád, O,) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoqN","text_ar":"رَيْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to the copies of the K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A scanty fall of rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus bearing two contr. meanings. (JK, Ibn-'Abbád, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17295","headword_ar":"رَيِّقٌ","root":"ryq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyqN","text_ar":"رِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also, (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoqN","text_ar":"رَيْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) which is a contraction of the former, sometimes used, (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ray~uwqN","text_ar":"رَيُّوقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AO, K,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most excellent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything, as, for instance, of youth, and of rain. (S.) [The first and second are also mentioned in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwq","text_ar":"روق"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. J cites here, and ascribes to Lebeed, as an ex. of the second of these words, a verse which I have cited in the third paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErD","text_ar":"عرض"},{"kind":"text","text":", but with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqa","text_ar":"رَوْقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoqa","text_ar":"رَيْقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from the TA, in which it is ascribed to ElBa'eeth.]"}],"source_refs":["S","K","AO"]},{"entry_id":"n17291","headword_ar":"رِيقٌ","root":"ryq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Saliva;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruDaAbN","text_ar":"رُضَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K, TA;) i. e. (TA) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water of the mouth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Msb, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEaAb","text_ar":"لُعَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water of the mouth in the early morning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part of the day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA: [but this rendering is often inapplicable:]) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water of the mouth while it is therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for when it has gone forth from the mouth it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buSaAqN","text_ar":"بُصَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buzaAqN","text_ar":"بُزَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busaAqN","text_ar":"بُسَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bSq","text_ar":"بصق"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyqapN","text_ar":"رِيقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, in poetry: (Msb, TA:) or this has a more particular meaning; (S, Msb, * K;) [i. e. it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat of saliva;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little saliva:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroyaAqN","text_ar":"اَرْيَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] (S, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyaAqN","text_ar":"رِيَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of mult.]. (TA.) [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboliEoniY riyqiY","text_ar":"اَبْلِعْنِى رِيقِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Suffer thou me to swallow my saliva;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"give thou me time to swallow my saliva:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blE","text_ar":"بلع"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grant thou me some delay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let me alone for a while,"},{"kind":"text","text":"that I may say, or do, such a thing. (Har p. 164.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AibotalaEa riyqah","text_ar":"اِبْتَلَعَ رِيقَه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He swallowed his saliva:"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he restrained his anger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blE","text_ar":"بلع"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uriba EalaY Alr~iyqi","text_ar":"شُرِبَ عَلَى الرِّيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was drunk in the state of fasting; before breakfast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:) and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ukila","text_ar":"اُكِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was"},{"kind":"text","text":"so"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eaten"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa EalaY Alr~iyqi","text_ar":"هُوَ عَلَى الرِّيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AO, S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY riyqihi","text_ar":"عَلَى رِيقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa ray~iqN","text_ar":"هُوَ رَيِّقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AO, S, K,) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fayoEilN","text_ar":"فَيْعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iqN","text_ar":"رَايِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is fasting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he has not breakfasted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu EalaY riyqK","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ عَلَى رِيقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY riyqi nafosiY","text_ar":"عَلَى رِيقِ نَفْسِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu ray~iqFA","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ رَيِّقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iqFA","text_ar":"رَايِقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fasting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not having eaten anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, TA.) [Hence also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyqu Al$~amosi","text_ar":"رِيقُ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", likewise called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEaAbu Al$~amosi","text_ar":"لُعَابُ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaATu Al$~amosi","text_ar":"مُخَاطُ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyqu Al$~ayaATiyni","text_ar":"رِيقُ الشَّيَاطِينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaATu Al$~ayoTaAni","text_ar":"مُخَاطُ الشَّيْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fine filmy cobwebs termed gossamer:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see arts."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lEb","text_ar":"لعب"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mxT","text_ar":"مخط"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strength:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remains of life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the spirit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the soul:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syns."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quw~apN","text_ar":"قُوَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaqN","text_ar":"رَمَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which latter, it should be observed, has both of these meanings, so that possibly only the former meaning may be here intended]. (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna h`*aA AlA^amoru wabinaA riyqN","text_ar":"كَانَ هٰذَا الاَمْرُ وَبِنَا رِيقٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This event happened when there was in us strength."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Msb","S","K","AO","ISk"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}